text: Hi Laura. That’s great it was your school! I was suppose to go but I couldn’t get out of work :( Sorry I don’t get to meet you. Were there other creative industries? Did you find the day interesting?

It's alright:smiley: you must have a busy schedule. There weren't really creative industries, mostly engineering and things like that. There was a guy who did game development but that was pretty much it.
The day was interesting but it's just not something I would like to work in in the future:sweat_smile:
